Updated the correct preview video You spoke we listened :D Say hello to a completely new Pic Blend.er Here s the new AWESOME Brand new app design 12 Blend Modes with a live preview Access to a Foreground Images library of over 400 images that will continuously grows with each update Efficiently erase areas of the foreground image using our new intuitive and user friendly Masking Tool Discover never seen before filters that will transform your photo into a Classic Camera look or Atrsy RGB look 200 Blend Effects such as Light Leaks Elements Swooshes even Fire and Smoke so many more. You can even select from 12 blend modes to make each effect become truly part of your photo New Exciting Movable Effects that you can drag and rotate to the perfect position Adjustment Tools such as: Enhance Brightness Contrast Crop Rotate Sharpness Hue Saturation Exposure Warmth Vignette with colors Pixellate Curves Credits: A BIG Thank You to Photographer Sid Scott and Super Model Lucerne for allowing us to their photo for the apps preview video. What s New: Hello our Pic Blender friend here s what you will get with this update Now you can see a tutorial on how the app works The app will be compatible for iPhone 5 as well. Also this app will work on Portrait mode as well. The eraser feature is also improved so now you can see where exactly your finger is on the Image. There are some new exicting categories of images.
